in order to survive in the world we have
little option but to spend our lives

00:00:04.910 --> 00:00:10.579
being rather defended that is at one
remove from are more vulnerable sides

00:00:10.579 --> 00:00:16.430
closed off from certain emotions focused
in many cases on not feeling

00:00:16.430 --> 00:00:20.870
and yet in relationships quite the
opposite is required to be good at love

00:00:20.870 --> 00:00:27.200
means to have a capacity to reveal one's hurt, desires and tender sides this is quite

00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:28.490
a balancing act

00:00:28.490 --> 00:00:32.689
great strength for most of the day and
well handled tenderness for the few that

00:00:32.689 --> 00:00:33.560
remain

